Content.Data:
//User_ Data// directory contains information about user credentials and configuration of this instance of TM.

{{/Image/user_datadir1.jpg}}

If enabled for User_Data, TEAM Mentor will automatically create a git commit for every change to user information. This includes user creation, deletion, change in user information and user activity as well as configuration changes.  By default //User_Data// git integration is switched off.  To enable git integration for //User_Data// add the following line to the //Library_Data\XmlDatabase\User_Data\TmConfig.config// configuration file in between the //<Git> </Git>//  tags.

{{{
   <Git>
    <AutoCommit_UserData>true</AutoCommit_UserData>
  </Git>
}}}

This will create the .git directory under //\Library_Data\XmlDatabase\User_Data// directory. 

{{/Image/gitUser_DataDir1.jpg}}

Please note that the git commits will remain local.
